{
  "stem": "24409.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's what it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "With, we ourselves, fell for the trick of [INAUDIBLE] calling it the Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But a few-- it was the 9th of November, a few days before, I believe on the 7th, but not earlier than the 6th of November, those would be on the train in [?",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Arnostadt. ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Arnostadt ?] was the border station between Austria and Italy, where we had been held up for so long.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Where all the new ships, these were to come.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "With the [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Davaris ?] and again, because it's a [INAUDIBLE] and a new ship, an old ship, but new in our service.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I believe on the two transports there were some 1,100 people, more than 1,100-odd people, who left Vienna just before this National Program, the so-called Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And taken through guards, through guards.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And guards, of course, you must know that Romania was a country which tries to live on bribery.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The government didn't pay the employees.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They had to get their money from bribery.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "When I arrived from Athens, my ship, in Constanta, I was one of the first ones out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there was absolutely kosher.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I didn't smuggle anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the man at the counter where we lined up, had the luggage there, asked me, do you have anything to declare.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I said, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He said, open your luggage.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So I opened it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He said, take the things out that you smuggled.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I say, I don't smuggle anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So he took the things and thew them in the air, like a fountain that came down.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And shouted to the other people, this is what happens if somebody claims he has nothing to declare.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
